Platform
BlueSource is a Cloud Native application. It is deployed in AWS. BlueSource is an Angular front end that reference Node APIs. Here is the initial Small Group Infrastructure Overview.
The PREP and PROD App and APIs are running in
•	Hardware/Software: m5.large running Amazon Linux ECS images (Docker 17.12.1-ce)
•	CPU and Memory: 2 vCPU/8GB RAM
•	Database: db.r4.large (2 instances in separate availability zones) hosting AWS Aurora MySQL databases.
•	Load Balancer is set up for PREP and PROD running in 2 instances of each service.

